mangaget README
---------------

Download manga chapters from mangafox.com

You must have these things on your PATH:
   * wget

To make a comic book archive for a comic reader, use the zip or rar tools to zip
up a volume directory.

Example usage (will download Rosario Vampire Season II chapters 1 to 35 inclusive,
into directory 'rosario_vampire_season_ii' in the current working directory):

    perl mangaget.pl --start=1 --end=35 \
      --url=http://www.mangafox.com/manga/rosario_vampire_season_ii/

TODO:
